  "description": "This fine apartment, located in an award-winning complex close to Puerto Banus, has been fully refurbished into a perfect holiday home. It is light, modern, well designed, and has a large terrace with ample space to relax!\n\nThe apartment provides a feeling of spaciousness with a modern open kitchen with a breakfast bar. That way, you can cook dinner whilst still having a nice chat with the people enjoying the living area. This part of the living room is fitted with a large and comfortable corner couch from where you can enjoy the smart TV. Furthermore, there are two bedrooms each with their own bathroom.\n\nFrom the living room, you step out onto the beautifully decorated outside terrace where you will find ample space to relax and switch off from all stress. There is a lounge corner and a large dining table.\n\nThe apartment is located in an award-winning complex that has many wonderful facilities as a luxury hotel complex would.\n\nThe tropical communal gardens are wide and well-maintained and offer 3 large pool areas and a poolside restaurant with a real pizza oven. An official reception, children’s club, and state-of-the-art gym with spa and indoor pool (extra fees) make this high-standard complex a complete package to enjoy it all.\n\nPuerto Banus is just a few minutes away and so is the heart of Marbella with its lovely old town center, the parks and of course the famous Promenade “Paseo Maritimo”.\n\nFor people who enjoy playing golf, there is a large number of high-class golf courses around, in a range of 2-10 minutes of driving. Furthermore, there are lots of activities available like water parks, and animal parks such as Selwo Marina in Benalmádena with dolphin shows or Selwo Aventura Safari Park in Estepona, a Butterfly park or watching Crocodiles in Torremolinos.\n\nPlease note that we welcome families and couples only, no groups under 30, and no hen or stag parties. Should you fall outside of this category but wish to book nonetheless, please send us an enquiry detailing a bit more about yourself and the group that you will be travelling with so we can request this for you.\n\nWe look forward to welcoming you!",
